OL,5, The grandfather of Merseyside shooting 
OL,6, victim Elle Edwards has urged family   
OL,7, and friends to live on with "hope" as  
OL,8, they gathered for her funeral.         
OL,10,FThe 26-year-old died after a gunman    
OL,11,Fopened fire at the Lighthouse pub in   
OL,12,FWallasey Village on Christmas Eve.     
OL,14,FShe was merely a bystander and not the 
OL,15,Fintended target, police said.          
OL,17,FThe vicar at the service at St         
OL,18,FNicholas' Church said Ms Edwards'      
OL,19,Fgrandfather George wanted everyone to  
OL,20,F"leave with hope in our hearts".       
